title: Carb Smart Smoky Paprika Chicken with a Veggie Medley
description: Sometimes all you need is a punchy spice to bring the whole meal together! Smoked paprika is our secret weapon in this chicken dinner. The bed of veggie medley ensures you're getting a mixture of all your favourite things.

